---
layout: page
title: Software
---

<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mb-8 -mt-4">Things I've built. Mostly Ruby on Rails and Hotwire.</p>

<div class="flex flex-col">
  <% collections.software.resources.sorted_by_launch_date.each do |project| %>
  <a href="<%= project.relative_url %>" class="py-4 border-b border-slate-100 last:border-0 group block">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between gap-6 mb-1">
      <span class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 group-hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors duration-150"><%= project.data.title %></span>
      <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 shrink-0"><%= project.data.type %></span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 m-0 leading-relaxed"><%= project.data.description %></p>
  </a>
  <% end %>
</div>
